            <li>‚Ä¢ E. coli and Enterococci readings are required</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Include rainfall data when available</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Values over 1000 CFU/100ml will show a warning</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Data Guidelines</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Safe levels: &lt; 100 CFU/100ml</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Caution: 100-1000 CFU/100ml</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Avoid contact: &gt; 1000 CFU/100ml</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Check recent entries before logging new data</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          <strong>Need help?</strong> Check the <a href="/admin/help" class="text-primary hover:underline">admin documentation</a> 
          or contact the project team for technical support.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Card>
  </main>
</Layout>